      <p>4K video represents the next generation in video resolution.</p>
      <p>The ultra high-definition video equals four times the resolution of what is currently known as 1080p Full HD. Yamaha’s new ’75 Series receivers all support 4K pass-through.</p>
      <p><img src="images/4k-video.jpg" width="100%" alt="4K Video"></p>
